sequenceDiagram
    participant Scorer as Ensemble Scorer
    participant AlertMgr as Alert Manager
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Kafka as Kafka (fraud.alerts)
    participant Dedup as Deduplication Engine
    participant Template as Alert Templates
    participant Notify as Notification Service
    participant Escalation as Escalation Engine
    participant Email as Email (SES)
    participant SMS as SMS (SNS)
    participant Webhook as Webhook (Slack/PagerDuty)
    participant Dashboard as Streamlit Dashboard

    Scorer->>AlertMgr: High/Critical risk detected
    AlertMgr->>Dedup: Check dedup window (60 min)
    
    alt Duplicate Alert
        Dedup-->>AlertMgr: Suppressed (existing alert open)
        AlertMgr->>PG: Log suppression event
    else New Alert
        Dedup-->>AlertMgr: Allow alert generation
        AlertMgr->>AlertMgr: Classify severity
        AlertMgr->>AlertMgr: Enrich with context<br/>(customer history, recent txns)
        AlertMgr->>PG: INSERT fraud_alerts (status=open)
        AlertMgr->>Kafka: Publish alert event
        AlertMgr->>Template: Render alert content

        alt Critical Severity
            Template->>Notify: Immediate notification
            Notify->>SMS: Send SMS to on-call
            Notify->>Webhook: PagerDuty incident
            Notify->>Dashboard: WebSocket push
        else High Severity
            Template->>Notify: Standard notification
            Notify->>Email: Send alert email
            Notify->>Webhook: Slack channel post
            Notify->>Dashboard: WebSocket push
        else Medium Severity
            Template->>Notify: Dashboard only
            Notify->>Dashboard: WebSocket push
        end

        Notify->>PG: Log delivery status

        Note over Escalation: Timer starts (15 min)
        
        alt Not Acknowledged within 15 min
            Escalation->>Escalation: Escalation triggered
            Escalation->>PG: Update alert severity (+1)
            Escalation->>Notify: Re-notify at higher level
        end
    end

    Dashboard->>PG: Analyst views alert
    PG-->>Dashboard: Alert details + context
    Dashboard->>PG: UPDATE status = investigating
    Dashboard->>PG: UPDATE status = resolved<br/>resolution_notes = "..."
    PG->>PG: Audit log entry
